review_text: Squirrels, pigeons and seagulls. The benches could do with a refit but otherwise it's ok.
Is a really small park, with easy access and good space to walk.
Nice place to smoke a Jay

(Translated by Google) The park as such has nothing more than four benches, tables and trees, but they organize concerts from time to time which makes it a pleasant meeting place for the neighbors and the enjoyment of music.

(Original)
El parque como tal no tiene nada mas que cuatro bancos, mesas y arboles pero organizan conciertos de vez en cuando lo que lo hace un agradable lugar de encuentro para los vecinos y el disfrute de la música.

(Translated by Google) Beautiful diversity of children's play module. Water games for the summer and ice rink for the winter.

(Original)
Belle diversité de module de jeu pour enfants. Jeux d'eau pour l'été et patinoire pour l'hiver.

(Translated by Google) A small park, very intimate show. Easy access, nice.

(Original)
Un petit parc , spectacle très intime . Facile d accès , agréable .

(Translated by Google) Very nice atmosphere and especially very safe

(Original)
Tres belle ambiance et surtout tres sécuritaire
